{"tid":1558941,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下大家最近有冇發過類似既夢？","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T15:32:40.000Z","uid":254818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5938412ab71ae3a10e980a6dfab4e7181b0510f4","tid":1558941,"uid":254818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:26:26.000Z","msg":"個夢境就係exactly宜加香港發生緊既事，呢三個月都有不斷出去仲行得幾前下，但都好好彩冇比狗捉，唔知係咪咁不斷積住d壓力係個夢入面出現返，我分享返自己個個先<br />\n<br />\n係個夢入面，我同平時一樣約埋班朋友出去遊行，而個遊行地點exactly係我屋企附近，但唔知點解一黎就封鳩哂，勁多防暴速龍係到捉人開槍打鳩人，有個速龍見到我就追鳩住我，咁我就一直跑一直跑，個速龍追我唔到，咁我就跑左出馬路，成條馬路都係警車，咁岩望到架車入面有個女警，佢陰陰嘴咁望住個倒後鏡對住我笑，仲慢慢落車想黎捉鳩我，我即刻又跑走諗住返屋企啦，點撚知一去到樓下大堂個位見到入面冇開燈，黑猛猛咁，咁我就打密碼一開門就有兩個黑社會拎撚住刀棍彈出黎，去到呢個位就嚇到醒撚左，訓係張床到唔敢郁，出撚哂汗，過左陣發現係夢先冇咁驚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前三個月間唔中都有發下呢種夢，但今次真係第一次嚇到醒撚左，明明自己已經唔算好前排拎盾擋既巴打，而自己又識調節返個情緒，但都會發呢種閪夢，到底最前線既巴打有幾大壓力呢？<br />\n<br />\n呢三個月香港人到底經歷左乜野先會連訓教都比狗搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be4971434036eaab77e3a2a8bc604158203d0b7","tid":1558941,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:28:00.000Z","msg":"有，發夢俾人拉，俾狗打"},{"pid":"bae732d0cd212178a3202d4d091c0797fe703cef","tid":1558941,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"試過夢境比速龍追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇醒咗"},{"pid":"8c2f6a5d893bc1eea2fdcb0045b0ffcd39d607a2","tid":1558941,"uid":114245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"試過發夢比popo打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94c50b84ce7105abd8457b38f811a07fd482376","tid":1558941,"uid":254818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲發過類似既前，一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b609e804b52d061c893199742195371ba8df980a","tid":1558941,"uid":254818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"想訓返個好教姐，咁都要搞鳩我，你班仆街防暴速龍，得屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7e3ebf987249b27affc53822fe12082b2cad05","tid":1558941,"uid":254818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"之前發夢嚇醒呢就比鬼怪搞既，宜加就比你班仆街搞，你睇下你地似乜撚野，保護市民喎，搞到個撚個見到你地都調轉頭走既，你話你地醜唔醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfec821a5f0429bf404f105e1ff6f8cf98864682","tid":1558941,"uid":254818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"應承我，呢世都唔好原諒班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94ac3d335b13e81cd6673a7982e1d21f93efd56","tid":1558941,"uid":5028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"試過發夢有popo 係我面前用手槍近距離打爆左前線手足個頭 <br />\n其他手足保護我擋住我唔比我救佢 <br />\n嚇+喊到醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bd0c5af85bb530d206f2a2c02f65ab494a63e2","tid":1558941,"uid":49979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"借個位同咁多位手足講<br />\n<br />\n你地留意下自己會唔會可能中左PTSD<br />\n<br />\n識醫生朋友係元朗開鋪 佢話一星期內就確診左3個PTSD<br />\n<br />\nPTSD有咩要素你google都搵到<br />\n<br />\n我淨係想講PTSD可以變到好恐怖"},{"pid":"0637f9e166e604d00195fbca3a74184b11e1a2ce","tid":1558941,"uid":254818,"like":0,"dis